{
  "name": "Receipt Scanner with Tax Tracking",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 🧾 Receipt Scanner & Tax Organizer\n\n### What this workflow does:\n1. Watches Google Drive for new receipts\n2. Extracts store, date, items, total\n3. Figures out if it's tax-deductible\n4. Assigns a category\n5. Logs to Receipt Database\n6. Adds deductibles to Tax Tracker\n\n### Perfect for:\n• Freelancers tracking expenses\n• Small business bookkeeping\n• Tax prep and deductions",
        "height": 340,
        "width": 280,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "049d6932-10d0-4970-a6f5-390de0140c74",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        0,
        128
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 💰 Tax Categories\n\n• Office Supplies\n• Business Meals\n• Travel\n• Equipment\n• Software\n• Professional Services\n• Marketing\n• Not Deductible",
        "height": 208,
        "width": 200
      },
      "id": "918d4a00-a2da-4530-83aa-582440676fb6",
      "name": "Sticky Note1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1424,
        -80
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### 1. Get receipt\nDownloads new files from Receipts folder",
        "height": 80,
        "width": 260
      },
      "id": "b72f914b-7200-4eb9-a709-c5b02f9a2ffb",
